data.description: Waterway Estates, No HOA. Gorgeous full-length, canal view from this renovated/remodeled 3 bedroom 2 bath, 1.5 car garage, SAILBOAT ACCESS, DIRECT GULF ACCESS home on over-sized, corner lot, plenty of room for RV pad. New Metal roof, new soffit, facia, gutters, new paint, new dock and lift with 10,000 lb capacity.   Diagonally laid tile flooring throughout home, Remodeled kitchen, custom cabinets, granite and an amazing view. New My Shower Door glass enclosures in bathrooms, new master bath vanity/counter, remodeled guest bath w/new tub, all new lighting/ceiling fans, remodeled laundry room, French doors to master bedroom, new Hot Water heater, new AC unit in converted family room, dual AC units. Brick-paver rear patio w/ room for a pool. New screen enclosure to patio and front porch. New driveway concrete paint/sealer. Crown molding, fresh paint, huge front and side yards with mature landscaping, well water sprinkler irrigation, workshop and storage building, and much more!
